column2: select top #  p.ra, p.dec, p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z, p.type,  p.isoA_u, p.isoA_g, p.isoA_r, p.isoA_i, p.isoA_z,  p.isoB_u, p.isoB_g, p.isoB_r, p.isoB_i, p.isoB_z,  p.isoPhi_u, p.isoPhi_g, p.isoPhi_r, p.isoPhi_i, p.isoPhi_z,  flag from PhotoObj AS p Join PhotoFlags as flag where  p.ra BETWEEN # AND # AND p.dec BETWEEN # AND #  AND (p.type = # OR flag(&&&) > #)
